extendedInfo.description: DINOSAURS, the most deadliest creatures of the world, longtime gone, but lots of research and interets among us to understand its world better.Did you know Dinosaurs first appeared approximately 230 million years ago, and were the dominant terrestrial living beings for 135 million years, from the beginning of the Jurassic (about 201 million years ago) until the end of the Cretaceous (66 million years ago).Did you know the CretaceousâPaleogene extinction event led to the extinction of most dinosaur groups at the close of the Mesozoic Era.They are the very interesting creatures to know. Here we bring the various dinosaurs and their unique pictures in Jigsaw puzzles, a photo matching puzzle where in you are supposed to align the various parts of the dinosaurs images to align and bring it to proper image.
